        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme “UDAN Yojana” is implemented by Uttarakhand Civil Aviation Development Authority, Government of Uttarakhand. The scheme aims to make air travel affordable and accessible for all citizens, enhance regional connectivity within Uttarakhand and promote tourism.\n<br>\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme aims to make air travel affordable and accessible for all citizens, enhance regional connectivity within Uttarakhand and promote tourism.",
        "benefits_md": "***Under this scheme, the minimum one-way fare per person for helicopter services on the following routes is:***\n\n1. Dehradun to Tehri:  ₹3,437.00\n1. Tehri to Srinagar:   ₹3,437.00\n1. Srinagar to Gauchar:  ₹3,437.00\n1. Gauchar to Srinagar:   ₹3,437.00\n1. Srinagar to Tehri:   ₹3,437.00\n1. Tehri to Dehradun:  ₹3,437.00\n1. Dehradun to Srinagar:  ₹3,992.00\n1. Srinagar to Dehradun:  ₹3,992.00\n1. Dehradun to Gauchar:  ₹3,649.00\n1. Gauchar to Dehradun:  ₹3,649.00\n1. Sahastradhara to Gauchar:  ₹4,150.00\n1. Gauchar to Sahastradhara:   ₹4150.00\n1. Sahastradhara to Chinyalisound:  ₹3150.00\n1. Chinyalisound to Sahastradhara:  ₹3150.00\n1. Dehradun to Haldwani / Pantnagar:  ₹6281.00\n1. Haldwani / Pantnagar to Dehradun:   ₹6281.00\n1. Pantnagar to Pithoragarh:   ₹5111.00\n1. Pithoragarh to Pantnagar:   ₹5111.00\n1. Pantnagar to Almora:   ₹3356.00\n1. Almora to Pantnagar:   ₹3356.00\n1. Almora to Pithoragarh:  ₹3356.00\n1. Pithoragarh to Almora:  ₹3356.00\n\n<br>\n\n",
